title: Dylan Ferrandis and Valentin Teillet at the Inter MX in St.
description:
Volcom MX rider Dylan Ferrandis won 2 out of 3 races this past Friday at the Inter MX in St. Vincent de Tyrosse.
He had to pass the win in the 3rd race to his team mate and also Volcom pilot Valentin Teillet after he went down and had troubles with his bike.
Check out this little clip:

- Music -

Song: "Yawn"
Artist: ASG
Release: ASG
